The global, regional, and national burden of gastro-oesophageal reflux disease 
in 195 countries and territories, 1990-2017: a systematic analysis for the 
Global Burden of Disease Study 2017.

GBD 2017 Gastro-oesophageal Reflux Disease Collaborators.

Collaborators: Dirac MA, Safiri S, Tsoi D, Adedoyin RA, Afshin A, Akhlaghi N, 
Alahdab F, Almulhim AM, Amini S, Ausloos F, Bacha U, Banach M, Bhagavathula AS, 
